summary:
This is a resource mod for X-wing Fighter by electionis

Adding more ships to that awesome mod
descriptionHtml:
The TIE fighter as a static object.  To add in game all you need to do is go into the Creation Kit and type StarWars or TIEFighter in the object window to find the new static object.  It has been Nav meshed all ready so you can climb on or jump off.

____________________________________ Installation+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

Use 7zip or WinRar to extract the files.
Move the Data folder to your Skyrim folder.

You can find the Skyrim folder here: Programfiles(x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\skyrim\data          FOR 64-bit users
You can find the Skyrim folder here: Programfiles\Steam\steamapps\common\skyrim\data                 FOR 32-bit users

Photoshop CS6

Enjoy and may the force be with you.
